# No harness HTML

Do not add committed test harness HTML pages. Browser debugging and parity use **headed Playwright** only.

## Prohibited

- New files under `ops/fixtures/harness/` (directory removed)
- `harnesshtmlmiddleware` or serving `*.html` test fixtures from `ops/fixtures/`
- Standalone debug HTML outside `cafe/` (e.g. `ops/fixtures/**/**.html` for Playwright hosts)

## Required instead

| Use case | Approach |
|----------|----------|
| Daisy/synth offline parity | Headed Playwright → `GET /parity-host` (inline COEP blank page) → `page.evaluate` + `ops/lib/daisy-parity/*-runner.ts` |

Shared helpers: [`tasks/lib/parity/parity-playwright.ts`](../../tasks/lib/parity/parity-playwright.ts) (`launchparitybrowser`, `parityhosturl`), [`tasks/lib/parity/harness-middleware.ts`](../../tasks/lib/parity/harness-middleware.ts) (`parityblankhostmiddleware` only).

## Examples

```text
❌ BAD — harnesshtmlmiddleware serving parity-regen.html
✅ GOOD — page.goto(parityhosturl(port)) + import runner in page.evaluate
```
